data.description: PRICE REDUCE  This is the moment you have found the house you were looking for with 4 bedrooms PLUS suite for the in-laws with separate entrance to the house on a beautiful well maintained brick ranch on almost an acre surrounded by farmland. Very convenient  to both US 1 and I-85 Enjoy with your friends and family in your private pool with beautiful views and a large back deck,Outside half bath next to the pool. Front porch with rocking chair perfect for enjoying views of mature oaks, maples, magnolias and pear trees throughout the property. This property is completely fenced New septic system Den's built-ins are from the former Heinz Pickle plant in Henderson, 150 years old
